data.description: Welcome to 24035 Hanover Street! This modern three-bedroom ranch is all about space. Interior is well kept with a galley kitchen and generously-sized living room for all your entertaining needs. Home almost doubles in livable square footage with a cozy fully-finished basement. Right outside the Telegraph corridor and close to everything. Would make a great starter home or investment property. Schedule your showing today and be moved in before spring. Updates: Roof (2022), Furnace (2018), Hot Water Tank (2019), Vinyl Windows. FINISHED BASEMENT.
